        <ontology:is_identified_by rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/appellation/Innovation"/>
        <ontology:partOfNarrative rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N49_VC_25_SER"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/43.20388780596991_22.639746604203296"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/1"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Endogenous and Exogenous. The carpets are marketed online and by order. There is an initiative to continue development of motives as they tell the contemporary story, but this has still not catch on. The innovation is related to New products, New processes, New marketing strategies and New governance systems. The land use systems involved are Forestry and Natural land. The local assets include Natural, social and cultural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


